OL,3,CStaffordshire couple lose out on
OL,4,Cwedding after Slater's Inn venue
OL,5,Cclosure
OL,7,FA wedding venue in Staffordshire has
OL,8,Fsuddenly closed, leaving dozens of
OL,9,Fcouples hoping to get married in a
OL,10,Ffinancial hole.
OL,12,F27-year-old Lorraine Slight, a nursing
OL,13,Fassistant at the Royal Stoke Hospital,
OL,14,Fhad hoped to tie the knot in June,
OL,15,Funtil she heard that her dream wedding
OL,16,Fvenue had closed.
OL,18,FShe and her fiance, Adam Goldwater had
OL,19,Falready paid almost #4,000 to the
OL,20,FSlater's Country Inn, which they now
OL,21,Fcannot get back.
