OL,7,FThis week, the venue in Balwin's Gate
OL,8,Fin Newcastle-under-Lyme, posted a
OL,9,Fnotice outside the building announcing
OL,10,Fthey were closed.
OL,12,F"We've lost all that money"
OL,14,FNow the couple say they are trying to
OL,15,Ffind a new venue they can afford.
OL,17,FLorraine says they now don't know when
OL,18,Fthey'll be able to get married, saying:
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/8
