OL,7,F"We've lost nearly four grand, it's so
OL,8,Fmuch, and we won't get that back at
OL,9,Fall.
OL,11,F"The venue pushed for us to pay via
OL,12,Fbank transfer, and we did that, and we
OL,13,Fwere very silly to do that really and
OL,14,Fwe didn't think... so we've lost all
OL,15,Fthat money and it's not affordable to
OL,16,Fget another wedding at all."
