OL,7,FShe says "It's taken a big toll on us
OL,8,Ffinancially, because we know we're not
OL,9,Fgoing to get that money back, and we
OL,10,Fsaved so hard for this wedding and set
OL,11,Fstuff back."
OL,13,FAdam added "It's just heartbreaking".
OL,15,FLorraine said she feels like the
OL,16,Fowners should face up to what's
OL,17,Fhappened, saying:
OL,19,F"The most annoying thing is that the
OL,20,Flaw allows people like this to get
OL,21,Faway with it.
