OL,7,F"It would just be nice for them to
OL,8,Fhave the decency and get in touch with
OL,9,Fus and just tell us what's going on."
OL,11,F"I've never ever cried so much in one
OL,12,Fday"
OL,14,FThe closure has also suddenly left
OL,15,Faround fifty staff out of work.
OL,17,FOne of those was Lexi Brown, 18, who
OL,18,Fwas a waitress at the venue.
