OL,7,FShe went on to say "My last shift was
OL,8,Fon Saturday, the restaurant was full,
OL,9,Fwe had a wedding on, everything was
OL,10,Fnormal. No one expected the news. It's
OL,11,Fjust come out of nowhere.
OL,13,F"We were told not to post anything on
OL,14,Fsocial media. I just feel so bad for
OL,15,Fthe customers who had weddings booked.
OL,17,F"Obviously they don't know what to do
OL,18,F- they know as much as we know, and we
OL,19,Fhave no idea what's going on.
