OL,7,F"There's about 48 or 50 staff. There's
OL,8,Fjust so much that's gone. You've got
OL,9,Fpeople with families, so many people
OL,10,Fin different situations and we don't
OL,11,Fknow what to do. We've been left
OL,12,Fstuck."
OL,14,FITV News Central has approached owners
OL,15,Fof the venue for comment.
